column8: Amet Actio Technology Ltd, which has registered in Delaware USA, is conducting various renewable energy development projects in fields such as biomass, solar, wind, hydro and geothermal in accordance with greenhouse gas reduction programs of UNFCCC (United Nations Framework Convention on Climate Change) which are Sustainable Development Mechanism (SDM) and Renewable Energy 100% (RE100) to prevent global warming.  AAT also develops an integrated Certified Emission Reductions (CERs) trading platform where the CERs are minted and converted to eCERs (electronic CERs) through Artificial Intelligence (AI) of Measurable, Reportable, Verifiable (MRV) system based on Distributed Ledger Technology (DLT).  Carbon market had restrictions in generating and trading CERs between countries and continents because of the Kyoto Protocol in 2005 but Conference of Parties (COP) held in Paris launched the New Climate Regime (Paris Agreement) in 2015. In response, AAT platform made a fundamental approach to address issues of environmental soundness, transparency, accuracy, completeness, comparability, accessibility and prevent double counting, which are important agendas of Article 6 of Paris Agreement. This solution will encourage more people to actively participate in the carbon market to reduce greenhouse gas. To this stand, as the first step, AAT is developing an incineration power generation project in Lombok, Indonesia from July 2022. The CER generated through this project will be converted to eCER and then traded as Offset on the AAT platform. This will be a direct solution for ESG management, carbon neutrality, and greenhouse gas reduction, which the international community is deeply concerned about.

Many people are in a constant battle with oral health diseases such tooth decay and gum issues, but have no idea how to win. When they go to their dentist, they are being bombarded with new cavities, deep gum pockets, and other problems. Many have to pay constantly for treatments. Most of the time, patients are only informed that they have cavities and gum disease, rather than how those cavities and gum disease might have occurred.  Denti-Pal aims to solve this problem on how to prevent cavities, maintain healthy gums, and help people take control of their oral health. That way patients can save time, money and preserve their overall oral well being. After all, oral health is the gateway to general health. 1.2. Describe the solution, Denti-Pal:  With Denti-Pal, the focus is on preventing tooth decay and other gum issues through the use of powerful dental products. Denti-Pal takes into account the patient's health history and habits in order to provide them with a diagnosis on how high their cavity and periodontitis risk is. For example, 25% of people between ages 65-69 are taking 5 or more prescription medications. Many of these medications cause xerostomia as a side-effect, which combined with poor habits leads to an extreme risk for developing cavities; most patients do not know their risk is this high. Patients with diabetes are also at high risk for bone loss, which accelerates tooth loss due to gum issues. Denti-Pal is able to calculate the cavity risk level using CAMBRA (developed by UCSF and UOP dental schools) as well as bring gum disease risk awareness.  With this knowledge, patients can get a dental package tailored to their risk level needs. Patients with a higher risk level tend to get cavities due to factors they cannot control (such as genetics) or factors they are unaware of being correlated (such as dry mouth). Denti-Pal addresses these factors directly with the product kit to create an effective solution in preventing cavities, stopping gum disease, and improving oral health. 2. Herbal-Pal <https://www.Herbal-Pal.org> 2.1. What specific problems do Herbal-Pal solve?  2.1.1. Many US patients lack understanding and easy access to traditional medicine. Conventional Western Medicine has limitations in treating disorders requiring a top-down holistic system as well as novel diseases such as COVID-19. 2.1.2. Well trained herbal medicine practitioners, such as traditional Chinese Medicine (TCM) doctors, are not allowed to “treat” COVID-19 patients in person by law in the US. Thus, US practitioners with experience healing COVID patients are concerned about legal troubles and do not want to publicize. However, they are willing to work with Herbal-Pal if we protect their licensure/business information, and take care of legal aspects while providing insurance.   2.1.3. Current healthcare system is costly and ineffective in prolonged war with COVID-19. While current mainstream allopathic medicine can solve some health issues, many conditions are still considered "incurable" or have “no special treatment”. Take COVID for example, mainstream media is anticipating vaccines to solve all problems, forgetting that vaccines are not for everyone. While early forms of vaccination were documented in 556 A.D., from TCM’s perspective, the immunization process only works for those who are healthy and strong. For those whose immune systems are not up to the extra burden, vaccines can shock the body by introducing “latent evils” and lead to unwanted consequences. 2.1.4. The one-size-fits-all mindset makes public health organizations reactive instead of proactive. They only take conservative, ineffective steps to avoid stepping on too many toes. For example, contrary to our early advocacy, the media and CDC have been changing faces about wearing masks.  2.2. Describe the solution, Herbal-Pal:  Herbal-Pal meets herbal medicine needs all in one spot. Patients are matched (based on specialties, availability, price range, and other nuances such as gender, languages spoken, former patient reviews) with curated traditional medicine doctors for remote consultations. Patients get personalized herbal prescription dispensed or patent formulae fulfilled and delivered anywhere. For those who have access to local herbal medicine doctors or herbs, they can choose to utilize part of Herbal-Pal service. Patients and providers will have a chance to leave multi-dimensional reviews for each other, and the feedback will become part of the underlying database.    The concept of Herbal-Pal is based on traditional medicine, with TCM being extensively used and well-documented among the world's medical traditions (e.g., Kampo in Japan, Ayurveda in India, complementary therapies in Switzerland, etc.). Most of the common health problems and many of the "incurable" issues can be treated with traditional medicine. Herbal-Pal currently offers a wide range of TCM doctors. We have seen some negative connotations coming from the media about TCM. In fact, just like how Arabic numbers do not have any political associations with Arabic countries, traditional Chinese medicine (TCM) is simply a name based on its location of origin. In fact, both traditional and modern medicines are pretty consistent although each has its advantages and limitations.    We believe far more US users can benefit from herbal medicine or the broader traditional medicine. The vision of Herbal-Pal is to become everyone’s personal traditional medicine consultant, like Upwork for herbal/ traditional/ integrative medicine. Remember to try out Denti-Pal & Herbal-Pal by WeCare Holistic. Your Wellness, We Care.

The advent and prominence of digital assets has created a market shift in the estate planning industry.  Unlike traditional estate assets, digital assets are intangible and constantly changing and evolving with new electronic files, devices, online accounts and ever-changing credentials. Today’s estate planning solutions have not kept pace and provide consumers with static solutions that can't effectively address their dynamic digital assets.  This gap represents a significant opportunity for a dynamic solution that addresses the unique needs of the modern digital estate. Noni was launched to solve this problem and fill a unmet need in today's estate planning industry.  Noni allows you to plan and manage what should happen to your digital assets and who should manage them in case of your death or incapacity securely and privately.  Noni keeps these plans current as your digital estate evolves.   If a life event occurs, Noni verifies the event and then securely distributes your final instructions to one or more of your appointed fiduciaries to carry out your final wishes for your Digital Estate.  Noni can also serve as your personal fiduciary for online accounts that you wish to have closed, relieving this burden from your loved ones.   Noni works with all existing Estate Plans and Traditional Estate Planning Solutions.

column8: Generally speaking, there is not a large scale solution for efficient cashless cannabis payments for the multi-billion dollar industry. Paying via debit at the PoS in CO, CA, and other more developed industries exists, however, these systems operate as disguised ATMs, and incur many different fees as a result. This leads to a markup of >$10-15 in most cases. Rhizomatiq is a DLT (Distributed Ledger Technology) Utility Token based on the DAG-Tangle architecture; this allows for high efficiency, resistance to attacks, environmentally green operations and most importantly an incredibly high throughput rate for instant transaction authorization. Built on top of the DLT is a suite of Supply Chain Track/Trace algorithms that provide transparency up the Cannabis Supply Chain for Regulators, Consumers, Suppliers, and Merchants alike. This suite is a logistics tracing mechanism, that follows batches of tested Cannabis products throughout the distribution process; from seed, to sale. Rhizomatiq aims to streamline this process, and act as a base for the Cannabis industry to build on. Due to the efficiency and scalability of the DAG-Tangle architecture, we are able to offer extraordinarily low fees (.25% S2M / $1 C2M per Tx), and instantly approved transactions. The process is simple and intuitive. SEND / RECEIVE transaction pairs represent completed "seeds". These seeds are stored on "nodes", our word for the Account Tangle architecture. Transactions on the node are verified using a standard Random Selection algorithm. Before either a SEND or RECEIVE transaction is sent, a dense regulatory compliance process is completed in which the Account Holder's ability to partake in the transaction is verified. Rhizomatiq Tokens are Utility Tokens, therefore transactions are initiated as payment transfers to and from the senders and receivers payment methods, respectfully, and the Tokens themselves will never be able to be Bought or Sold.
